Interface IPlaylist

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EphemeralPlaylist, SavedPlaylist

    public interface IPlaylist
    This class must be used by any kind of playlist.

    • Method Detail

      • addTrack

        boolean addTrack(Track track)
        Add a track to the playlist. It also create a PlaylistTrack to link the Track and the playlist (for DB purpose).
        Parameters:
        track - The track to add to the playlist.
        Returns:
        true if the track was added false otherwise.

      • contains

        boolean contains(Track track)
        Check if a track is already contained in the playlist or not.
        Parameters:
        track - The track to check in the playlist.
        Returns:
        true if the track was found false otherwise.

      • getPlaylistTrack

        PlaylistTrack getPlaylistTrack(Track track)
        Get the PlaylistTrack object where the Track is the one passed by parameter.
        Parameters:
        track - The Track which we will search in the PlaylistTrack list.
        Returns:
        The PlaylistTrack object where the Track is the one passed by parameter, `null` otherwise.

      • getTracksList

        Get the tracks of the playlist.

      • isSaved

        Check if the playlist is saved or not.
